data.description:
Location, Location, Location!  This home is in the country but only a couple minutes from town.  You will love the spacious kitchen that is open to the living room making family time & entertaining a treat.   New appliances, updated kitchen, new flooring & so much room to spread out yet have your own individual space!   If you don't need 6 bedrooms, you can have his & her offices, gym, craft room, etc. 
There's a lean-to for the animals (perfect for hobby farm), over-sized 2 car garage & lots of parking. Pending with 72 Hr 1st Right of Refusal.
